"26:33:6" : {s: 26, a: 33, w: 6, r: "نظر", t: "لِلنَّٰظِرِينَ", l: "نَٰظِرِين", lc: 5, tl: "lilnnāẓirīna", lb: "অপেক্ষাকারী",e: "for the observers", b: "দর্শকদের জন্য", f: 3, rm: "to see, look at, glance, gaze, observe, behold, consider, regard, listen to, be patient towards, wait, contemplate, grant respite, put off, scrutinise, show kindness, examine, search, reflect. nazara - the look with affection, to perplex, dazzle."},
